-- Abu Dhabi's Mubadala, Prudential Unit Form Venture for Property Investment
-- Arif Sharif
-- 2010-07-14T05:47:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/abu-dhabi-s-mubadala-prudential-unit-form-venture-for-property-investment.html

          
          
             Mubadala Development Co., an Abu
Dhabi government-backed investor, and a unit of Prudential
Financial Inc. agreed to form a joint venture company to invest
in real-estate projects.  
 Pramerica Real Estate Investors and Mubadala formed the
venture to “raise capital from investors to fund and invest in
real estate projects in Abu Dhabi and other global markets,”
Mubadala said in an e-mailed statement today.  
